Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.44,0:01:17.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.26,0:01:19.51,Dial-CH,,0,400,0,,這都什麼跟什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.12,0:01:19.90,Dial-CH,,500,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.09,0:01:23.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.79,0:02:58.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「血型小測試」
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.73,0:03:02.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,提問
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.38,0:03:04.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我的血型是什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.83,0:03:05.47,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,為什麼要問我
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我感覺你可能會好奇
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.38,0:03:13.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,所以你知道嗎 我猜你肯定不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.89,0:03:16.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,從印象上來判斷是O型
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不過她這表情 答案可能不走尋常路
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那就是最不可能的A型
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.76,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但也有可能是B
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,別急
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.37,0:03:27.02,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,依我的經驗來看 像我姐那種B血型人
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.02,0:03:29.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是不會自己主動聊起血型話題的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.91,0:03:32.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,因為會遭受不正當迫害
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.14,0:03:36.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,用血型判斷他人性格的人 多半是狗屎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我先套點線索出來吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我是AB型來著
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,天才血型
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,上鈎了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.06,0:03:47.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哪有人會說自己是天才啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.65,0:03:48.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.92,0:03:50.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我懂了 妳是A型
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可惜
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我是AB
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,對啊 山田是這樣的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.63,0:03:58.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我們血型一樣呢
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.18,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,啊 其實我撒謊了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.43,0:04:02.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我不是AB
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.76,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那你是什麼血型
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.18,0:04:08.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,別聊血型了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.63,0:04:10.47,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,知道了也沒什麼用
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.69,0:04:13.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,人的性格也不能簡單地分成4種
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,感覺也只有日本人有這種迷信
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.24,0:04:17.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.01,0:04:19.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,市川是B型
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「暗之能力者」
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.19,0:04:37.22,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,讓我媽給我買了偏大一點的運動衫
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.76,0:04:39.40,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,過不了多久就會長高的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也對 畢竟初中生嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.46,0:04:43.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,媽 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,很有暗之能力者的風範
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,然後那個3分就進了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.69,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,超常發揮
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,運氣球啦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.07,0:04:58.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,雖然那一球之後
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.57,0:05:01.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,到終場哨聲響起前 我都再沒摸到過一次球
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.35,0:05:02.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,奇蹟的小林子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.63,0:05:03.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,努力過就好啦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.70,0:05:06.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,只要奇蹟一直發生 它就不再是奇蹟了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,妳真的行嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.41,0:05:08.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.61,0:05:13.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我忘東西了 妳們先走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.10,0:05:13.92,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,妳… 妳幹嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.44,0:05:27.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,還以為你這衣服是跟別人借的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,別這樣 外人一看還以為妳打劫呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.12,0:05:31.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那你把手伸出來
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,暗中交易
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.06,0:05:43.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,萬一被發現了 受處分的人是我
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.58,0:05:44.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我不能收
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.46,0:05:45.71,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.73,0:05:49.54,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,反正是空的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.61,0:06:27.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「喜歡的髮型」
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.15,0:06:33.71,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,男生最喜歡的女生髮型
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是單馬尾哦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.26,0:06:36.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,萌子說的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.18,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也看人吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.64,0:06:43.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那市川喜歡什麼樣的髮型呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.64,0:06:47.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不可否認 單馬尾是很棒
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但雙馬尾也挺好
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.54,0:06:50.72,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不 波波頭也好
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可是普通的短髮也難以割捨
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.79,0:06:57.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不行 越想越覺得什麼髮型都很好
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,根本選不出來
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.67,0:07:01.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,深思熟慮
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.27,0:07:05.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我覺得妳什麼髮型都好看啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.87,0:07:10.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不是 我沒問什麼髮型好看
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.50,0:07:12.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,問的是你喜歡哪種
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.86,0:07:21.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「換教室」
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,唉 該走了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我有東西忘拿了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,妳這是啥都沒拿啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.23,0:07:45.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.40,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我幫你拿著
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.50,0:07:52.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,她這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.22,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼是妳啊 田山
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.72,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,在這裡幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,等朋友而已啦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.28,0:07:59.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,朋… 朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.49,0:08:01.74,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,下節課在化學教室？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我們班也在那邊上 一起過去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.34,0:08:07.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,糟了 這兩個人加上山田再加上我
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.82,0:08:09.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,空氣中必將瀰漫著尷尬
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,老師先前叫我
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,讓我先去趟辦公室來著
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.27,0:08:18.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼老是被老師罵呀
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,長點心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.05,0:08:23.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也是啊 換教室上課
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,她肯定是不想讓人知道 是和我一起去的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.22,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,原來她是要和我一起去啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.85,0:08:34.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.65,0:08:41.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「僵屍過家家」
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.93,0:08:45.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,如果我成了僵屍 你能對我下殺手嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.74,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 能吧…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.15,0:08:52.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好像是破壞了頭部才能讓僵屍死透吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那… 那如果
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.43,0:08:58.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我還維持著自我意識呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.63,0:08:59.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,劇情太老套了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這種時候但凡猶豫就會死
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,還是早點殺了好
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.66,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好麻煩啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.52,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不能出去
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.52,0:09:20.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,還是能說話的僵屍？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我能持槍嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,服了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.63,0:09:36.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怪了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我… 我得殺了她啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.69,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,必須趕緊動手
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.47,0:10:00.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哎喲 開槍開得太晚了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.63,0:10:03.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,為什麼為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.81,0:10:07.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山田死了 我也不活了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.67,0:10:10.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.28,0:10:12.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你現在
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,在幹嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.05,0:10:15.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,沒在幹嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.04,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那你猜
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我在做什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.48,0:10:29.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你想想
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.07,0:10:34.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「和老姐購物」
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.66,0:10:46.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山田要是穿上這種衣服 應該好看
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,把妳殺了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,選好了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.03,0:10:58.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山田的話
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,貪吃牛排套餐 超大份薯條
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.30,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再來份草莓醬鬆餅
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,兒童套餐在這裡哦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.01,0:11:10.59,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,很癢的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.67,0:11:14.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,又沒什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你真壞
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.52,0:11:17.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,來 張嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.72,0:11:24.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,如果山田有了男朋友 她也會這樣嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.23,0:11:25.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,來 張嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.53,0:11:31.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我看你一直盯著別人看
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.53,0:11:32.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,以為你也想模仿呢
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.86,0:11:35.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,把妳殺了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.28,0:11:38.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.51,0:11:42.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「肉包子」
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.66,0:11:51.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,買哪個呢
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.70,0:11:52.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我要披薩包
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.86,0:11:53.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那我也
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.43,0:11:55.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.86,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那我換成肉包
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.85,0:12:02.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就不和我吃一樣的是吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.26,0:12:05.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.01,0:12:09.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,買的時候啥也沒想 現在才發覺
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.92,0:12:11.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次自己買零食
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.09,0:12:12.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.82,0:12:13.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.07,0:12:14.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.15,0:12:16.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.40,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不會有學校裡的人經過吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.77,0:12:23.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,店員或者誰打小報告的可能性也…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.99,0:12:29.21,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哎呀 沒人會經過的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.79,0:12:33.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.19,0:12:35.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,暖暖的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.15,0:12:56.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.02,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,還行
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,看 買不一樣的就是有這種好處
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.69,0:13:12.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.00,0:13:18.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可能明天就去世了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.82,0:13:26.81,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「香味」
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,用完了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.43,0:13:43.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,老姐的 反正用了也沒人知道
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.44,0:13:47.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我聞到了女人的味道
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,還真有
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,一聞就能聞出來
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.69,0:13:54.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我太慘了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這氣味應該已經散了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.31,0:14:01.99,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你有沒有聞到一股香味
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,她也聞到了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就是很好吃的那種
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.55,0:14:08.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,造成奇怪的誤會也不好
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,還是老實告訴她吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.57,0:14:13.29,Dial-CH,,600,0,0,,因為我不小心用了我姐的洗髮液…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.71,Dial-CH,,0,600,0,,這家人今晚吃的是咖哩呢
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.77,0:14:17.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這家人今晚吃的是咖哩呢
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.96,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,啊… 呃 我用了我姐的洗髮液
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.97,0:14:23.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我聞聞
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.27,0:14:28.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.61,0:14:31.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不過今天上了體育課 有點聞不出來了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.79,0:14:33.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.07,0:14:38.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「偷懶」
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.29,0:14:43.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,大大大雞雞
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.87,Dial-CH,,600,0,0,,甩啊甩啊甩
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.86,0:14:45.87,Dial-CH,,0,500,0,,這人好煩
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.87,0:14:47.16,Dial-CH,,0,500,0,,離老娘遠點
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.87,0:14:48.10,Dial-CH2,,600,0,0,,衝破小內內
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,拖不乾淨
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.80,0:14:53.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,沒勁 好想回家啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.90,0:14:56.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,衛生讓保潔員來搞不好嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那要不然
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.71,0:15:00.09,Dial-CH2,,0,0,0,,夜晚仍堅挺
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.84,0:14:59.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,偷懶吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,夠了 閉嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.56,0:15:02.20,Dial-CH2,,0,0,0,,幹嘛幹嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.61,0:15:04.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你這是性騷擾了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.22,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這也算？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.13,0:15:10.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要是沒人搞衛生 就只能一直髒著了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.40,0:15:21.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,行 乾淨了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,其他地方也不髒
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.91,0:15:27.04,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,收工吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.16,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,收工了 就不算偷懶了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.26,0:15:40.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,拿她沒轍
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你想去哪
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但總之去個沒人的地方吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.04,0:15:48.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,別人在搞衛生 不能礙事吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.86,0:15:56.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.04,0:16:00.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.82,0:16:05.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,都幾點睡
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.37,0:16:05.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,平時
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.94,0:16:07.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,1點左右
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.52,0:16:09.21,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,太晚了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.90,0:16:10.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,壞孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.76,0:16:12.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.04,0:16:13.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,妳呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,11點半
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這不都過了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,都怪你
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.67,0:16:31.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「僵屍過家家2」
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.26,0:16:41.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我在想如果你變成了僵屍 我能下殺手嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不知道 殺吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.79,0:16:44.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我有不好的預感
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,來試試吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.53,0:16:47.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,行吧行吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.90,0:16:59.60,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你快開始啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我在演啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.87,0:17:02.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.47,0:17:04.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.79,0:17:07.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,經她這麼一說 我這確實和平時也沒區別
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.21,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.63,0:17:12.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但萬一你真的變成僵屍了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.30,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我要怎麼分辨你變沒變呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.73,0:17:15.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.71,0:17:18.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,比如聞聞氣味
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,或者聽聽心跳
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.81,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,靠近了就太危險了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,對哦
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.32,0:17:26.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那就看你能不能說出我的名字 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.09,0:17:27.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.99,0:17:36.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有可能忘不了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.84,0:17:40.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.67,0:17:46.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我就下不了手了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.81,0:17:54.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「拜拜」
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.86,0:17:58.72,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.23,0:18:00.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,拜…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.99,0:18:09.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,拜…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.34,0:18:13.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,從我嘴裡說出拜拜太噁心了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.77,0:18:14.99,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,噁心 別
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.04,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.07,0:18:23.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,回頭
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.75,0:18:25.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,見
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.38,0:18:31.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 明天見
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山田啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.16,0:18:37.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,明天可是週六
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.74,0:18:40.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.77,0:20:15.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「聖誕老人紅靴子」
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,看起來聖誕節快到了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.79,0:20:26.66,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,四川
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.55,0:20:31.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,來 這個給你
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.78,0:20:32.46,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.10,0:20:35.16,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但反正給的是垃圾 心知肚明了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.95,0:20:37.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那玩意我好像能穿上
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.02,0:20:38.46,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,試試
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.98,0:20:40.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,穿不上的吧 這很硬的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.45,0:20:42.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,都說了穿不上
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,肯定塞不進去
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.32,0:20:48.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,什麼什麼 這什麼情況
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.55,0:20:50.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這什麼情況
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.91,0:20:53.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好緊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.32,0:20:54.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,快進去了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.39,0:21:01.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也是 人生就是什麼都要嘗試
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.37,0:21:06.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,聖誕快樂
